sections.text:
This Act shall apply to all securities heretofore created or issued in the United Kingdom on behalf of the Government of Northern Rhodesia or hereafter created or issued in the United Kingdom on behalf of the Government of Zambia—
(a) in which a trustee might at any time have invested by virtue of section 2 of the Colonial Stock Act, 1900, of the Parliament of the United Kingdom; or
in which a trustee might at any time have invested by virtue of section 2 of the Colonial Stock Act, 1900, of the Parliament of the United Kingdom; or
(b) by the conditions of issue of which it is provided that the provisions of this Act shall apply to them;
by the conditions of issue of which it is provided that the provisions of this Act shall apply to them;
